06502,"uid":393145,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:13:06.000Z","msg":"蒙古人打一針可以任何地方食飯<br />\n色目人打兩針可以食飯 但打一針就食粥<br />\n打咗針既蒙古人食飯而隔離漢人冇打針 蒙古人可以打撚死佢<br />\n但如果個漢人有打針 就只可以打到佢半死50% 手腳只可斷一<br />\n呀 如果個蒙古人打齊兩針喇喎 就可以打到條友75%死 可以打斷四肢其中三肢<br />\n如果間食店老闆員工都係打咗兩針既蒙古人 咁就可以喺個安全區度打死佢100%<br />\n但如果老闆員工只打一針 咁又要扣返10%"},{"pid":"678dd0af9bb3937143d72a8ba2fbb72a3e1a06c1","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"9cd48722e58cb1da9d84a3c4cfce78bc1ac2857a","tid":2506502,"uid":303805,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"高貴既馬萊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVS4141rgosyvJpEEot5QuyvYhLX2fstzSW2G17PSspAh?filename=n73cZNP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn73cZNP.png&h=52aea407&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c0fe3a10b36b305eea9b63563b856f2bdf097e","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0807348c4041fe5a4bbc9c05ecb0f496dd337d48","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"呢件事好緊要，推推先"},{"pid":"47f749ae257469246dc348271bd42f946493be74","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:20:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4328aef988231bf64942f3c5b25bde5366af51c3","tid":2506502,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"318071105d41798a14c63dfbdf74bd2d4a5938fd","tid":2506502,"uid":275572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74bdf73609cbc673f0ca6cde96f6ab084b02f08b","tid":2506502,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:10:18.000Z","msg":"安心回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cl